<div class="container">
<h1> Welcome to Sinatra Stables </h1>
 <img 
  src="images/anna-kaminova-stables-unsplash.jpg" 
  class="img-responsive main-image"
  title="stables"
  width="80%" 
  height="50%"
  >
  <div class="col-md-8 col-md-offset-2">
    <h2>Board your horses at Sinatra stables!</h2>

    <h3>All horses currently boarding here:</h3>
    <ol>
    <% @horses.each.with_index(1) do |horse, index| %>
      <li><a href="/horses/<%=horse.id%>"><%=index%><%=horse.name%></a></li>
    <%end%>
    </ol>

    <div class="content">
      Here you can add as many horses as you like to Sinatra stables along with horse riders. <br><br>
      This app can be used by horse owners to help them keep track of what horses they have and which riders are exercising/competiting on each horse. <br><br>
      To get started <a href="/signup">Sign Up</a> or <a href="/login">Log In</a>.
      <br><br>
    </div>
    
    

    <br><br> <br><br> <br><br> <br><br> <br><br> <br><br>

  </div>
</div>
